===环境===
波城境内的环境和可持续发展事务由{{link-fr|波城城市圈公共社区|Communauté d'agglomération Pau Béarn Pyrénées}}负责。2015年，波城市区内共有5家污染企业<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.linternaute.com/actualite/pollution/pau/ville-64445 |title=Pollution à Pau (64000) : les chiffres |accessdate=2019-11-21 |language=fr |website=linternaute.com |quote=Pau possède 5 sites pollués sur son territoire |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421235913/http://www.linternaute.com/actualite/pollution/pau/ville-64445 |archive-date=2019-04-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，当年的一氧化碳浓度为340µg/m³、二氧化氮浓度为32µg/m³、悬浮颗粒物（PM10）22µg/m³，均略高于法国平均水平<ref name="pollution">{{cite web|url=http://www.linternaute.com/actualite/pollution/pau/ville-64445/pollution-air|title=Pollution de l'air à Pau (64000)|access-date=2019-08-01|website=linternaute.com|language=fr|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504044834/http://www.linternaute.com/actualite/pollution/pau/ville-64445/pollution-air|archive-date=2019-05-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===治安===
波城市区内共有一个派出所<ref>{{cite web |url=https://demarchesadministratives.fr/commissariat-police/pau-64000 |title=COMMISSARIAT DE POLICE À PAU 64000 |access-date=2019-11-21 |language=fr |website=demarchesadministratives.fr |archive-date=2020-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018013907/https://demarchesadministratives.fr/commissariat-police/pau-64000 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、一个国家宪兵队<ref>{{cite web |url=https://demarchesadministratives.fr/gendarmerie/pau-64000 |title=GENDARMERIE À PAU 64000 |access-date=2019-08-01 |website=demarchesadministratives.fr |language=fr |archive-date=2020-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018013902/https://demarchesadministratives.fr/gendarmerie/pau-64000 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和一个消防站<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sdis64.fr/contact/|title=CONTACT|access-date=2019-11-21|language=fr|website=sdis64.fr|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119151045/http://www.sdis64.fr/contact/|archive-date=2019-01-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

